    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 Coupe, finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This specimen is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, showing exceptional compression across all cylinders. The mechanical integrity is superlative; a comprehensive VANOS overhaul has been performed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, while the limited-slip differential remains quiet and responsive. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, maintaining its signature handling profile. With zero paint metered outside factory tolerances and a flawless interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this E46 represents the pinnacle of the analog M-car era.",
