      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. The factory 19-inch forged wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires. Inside, the cabin still retains its new-car scent; the Black Dakota leather seats feature crisp blue stitching and show zero bolster wear, maintaining their original matte factory finish. Every electronic component, from the Harman Kardon premium sound system to the navigation, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is stock and untouched, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
